# Sales & Outreach Rules

## Current outreach system

- Cold email via Zoho Mail API (ZohoMCP connected)
- Python scripts in outreach/ handle: CSV loading, dedup against Supabase, payload generation, send logging
- Target: Romanian food business owners — cafés, restaurants, takeaway, patisseries
- Cities: București, Cluj, Timișoara, Iași, Brașov, Constanța

## Email rules

- Always check Supabase (via MCP) for existing signups before adding to outreach CSV
- Never send to an email that already exists in auth.users
- Zoho daily send limit: respect it — do not batch more than the account allows
- All cold emails in Romanian — conversational, not corporate

## ICP scoring (for qualify-lead skill)

- Score 1–10
- High (8–10): 3+ locations, owner or ops manager role, food business
- Mid (5–7): 1–2 locations, owner, food business
- Low (1–4): wrong industry, employee not owner, outside Romania

## Partner channel

- Partners are: contabili, FiscalNet integrators, POS resellers
- Commission: 20% recurring + setup fee split
- Partner onboarding triggers: Loops "partner_signup" event
